name: Custom OOAK dog collar MEDIUM
description:
All collars are READY TO SHIP!!

Pet Couture is made from 100% recycled, discarded, vintage costume jewelry, so each collar is unique & one of a kind.. Quality collars are used to complete the look & are secured with long lasting epoxies..I have seen similiar styles are upscale boutiques that retail over $90+ each and still do not stand up as well as my collars do..

Collars are hand embellished with items that are choosen for their beauty and quality.. I have several styles & colors currently on Etsy, if you see one you like, please be sure to buy it now.. As each piece is made once and will not be duplicated..

Collar fits: Medium (buckle closure)
Length; 11" to 14" 
Width; 5/8"

Collar Color: Double layered pet friendly metallic pink pleather
Bling Includes: Rhinestones, Antique necklace pieces, & Gorgeous aurora borealis PINK recycled earring

name: Custom Pet Bling Small 7" to 10"
description:
"Silver Diamonds & Pearl" dog collar.. Turn your pet into a bow WOW!!! :)~ 

Pet Couture is made from 100% recycled, discarded, vintage costume jewelry, so each collar is unique & one of a kind.. Quality collars are used to complete the look & are secured with long lasting epoxies..I have seen similiar styles are upscale boutiques that retail over $90+ each and still do not stand up as well as my collars do..

Collars are hand embellished with items that are choosen for their beauty and quality.. I have several styles & colors currently on Etsy, if you see one you like, please be sure to buy it now.. As each piece is made once and will not be duplicated..

Collar fits: Small (toy breeds)
Length; up to 7" to 10"
Width; 3/8

Collar Color: Silver pleather buckle closure
Bling Includes: High sheen crystal rhinestones recycled earrings, buttons, faux pearl cabochon tiny button...

Cleaning your collar.. The best way to clean your collar is to get an old toothbrush, regular soft (Hand, anti baceterial) soap & gently scrub, allow to sit out to dry..

Sure once in a whilte your pet may loose a bling or too.. General wear on a pet collar is normal.. But I check each collar after they've cured for a week minimum to make sure everything has been placed & is strong enough even for the toughest wear.. My own 5 pets (who are my fav. models) wear my collars..

 **The bling at the closure is new to my collars. Has not been tested for durability, it may come off..
